text: Henry Nyandoro (October 20, 1969 in Kisii – August 28, 1998) was an international Kenyan football midfielder who played for AFC Leopard (1987-1990) and Shabana from 1990 to 1996 in Kisii. ==International career== He played 102 international matches for Kenya.
